description: **OFFER ACCEPTED, OPEN HOUSE CANCELED.** This beautiful two-bedroom, two-bathroom home is situated perfectly near all that Broadway has to offer: the thriving Seaport, South End, and convenient public transportation. This cozy condo boasts a large living room with an electric fireplace, a small breakfast nook/office space, and a kitchen with updated appliances and plenty of cabinet storage. The second bedroom works great as an office, nursery, or guest bedroom. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom, a walk-in closet, and access to your private deck overlooking a quiet park. Enjoy in-unit laundry, basement storage, blue-tooth-enabled surround sound, and "Smart-home" technology with an Ecobee heating/cooling system. Excellent opportunity to purchase in ever-growing South Boston!
